Frostlake Fortress has been secured from the cold!

'[placeholder], we have been attacked!

'The hardship of building our fortresses has been for naught. Today was to be our yearly tradition, The Battle at Frostbluff, you see. We have been making our forts the best they could be. Now we have had to cancel our throwing of snow and laughter, for a cold and evil wind has come to Winterhome.

'It is too cold to play and throw snow. I do hope that you will be able to help us fight off the cold so that we may have fun on this great winter's day.

'Let us reclaim the <rgb=#FF00FF>Tower of Grumpwood</rgb>!'
Capture Fortress of Frostlake!
A dreadful cold has come down from the mountains!
Talk to Una

'I can not speak on the queen's behalf for I am merely a squire. I have heard the rumours that a bold [placeholder] was to assist the <rgb=#FF00FF>Realm of Cluckland</rgb>.\n\n'If you succeed, we shall sing songs of the day!'
'Bok... bok!'
'My <rgb=#FF00FF>Fortress upon Frostlake</rgb> is under siege! When the moment is right, we must reclaim my keep!'\n\n'I am the King of Frostbluff, and I decree this!'
